snippet: Private Bradley Manning has notified a court-martial judge that he may plead guilty to at least some of the accusations that he leaked hundreds of thousands of military and diplomatic documents.
abstract: Private Bradley Manning notifies court-martial judge that he may plead guilty to at least some of the accusations that he leaked hundreds of thousands of military and diplomatic documents to antisecrecy group WikiLeaks.
lead_paragraph: Private Bradley Manning has notified a court-martial judge that he may plead guilty to at least some of the accusations that he leaked hundreds of thousands of military and diplomatic documents.

headline.seo: Private Bradley Manning Offers Partial Plea in WikiLeaks Case
headline.main: Private Accused of Leaks Offers Partial Guilty Plea
headline.print_headline: Private Accused of Leaks Offers Partial Guilty Plea
